he perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"55a282b45644c7c1cfacbfa0102f32b7fea9cc99","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c1db7567453483e09bdd935e7babffc76e2b3573","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fea3c197c6980cca66a1656e2bb4a7ab143b5846","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"558ae38c000e71569a19ac0fb3adf2870554b45b","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c85444474f084080f86a7075fe2f9d9333f28334","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2244452bc2372ecf8bb25ec9767e4404c20a9274","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e0fa39ea90304c3ef8554090d9a37819ea8dfb96","tid":1550403,"uid":201445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3e98c38dc44b32c29bfaeba0950937c898a08a99","tid":1550403,"uid":279091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"［文宣入］英文口號 聽日一齊大大聲嗌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550358\" da